snippet.title: Mysterious Neo Geo Prototype (Dragon's Heaven?) in Action (1 of 2)
snippet.description:
From Midwest Gaming Classic, NeoTurfMasta of the Neo Geo forums reveals an unknown, incomplete fighting game — which has been released to the general public. It is believed to be a work-in-project called Dragon's Heaven, produced by Face with ex-Technos staff. See http://www.usgamer.net/articles/a-mysterious-neo-geo-prototype-hits-the-web for more!

For more content like this, visit http://www.usgamer.net/
